{"tid":1518792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國正式設太空司令部　特朗普稱要確保太空主導地位","createTime":"2019-08-30T10:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T11:14:32.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5b29f01bd99a84bd01ce0fdf2197e29a49716db7","tid":1518792,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:58:11.000Z","msg":"美國正式設太空司令部　特朗普稱要確保太空主導地位<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477756-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477756-20190830.htm&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUir9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=810df203\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477756-20190830.htm&h=808f9570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477756-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普宣布，正式成立「太空司令部」，代表太空在美國國家安全和國防中，處於中心地位，將確保美國在太空的主導地位，永遠不受「質疑和威脅」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又說，「太空司令部」成立後，「太空軍」將在不久之後，成為美國第六大軍種，「太空軍」將組織、訓練和裝備部隊，支持「太空司令部」。<br />\n<br />\n白宮在聲明說，「太空司令部」將整合各軍種的力量，包括通信、情報、導航、導彈監測預警等優勢，形成作戰力，確保美國擁有不受限制地進入太空，及在太空自由行動的能力。"},{"pid":"2e9a61217cd92dbf0b0128248a8eae8f9f9c5957","tid":1518792,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUQvG7y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUQvG7y.gif&h=0b84475f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUir9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=483a3b4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUir9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=213a6ee0\" target=\"_